   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener> 
               <salute>Dear friend</salute>
            </opener>
         <p>I have the present <choice><sic>opertunity</sic><corr>opportunity</corr></choice> to drop you a few lines to let you now that I am well and have got safe to the <choice><sic>regment</sic><corr>regiment</corr></choice> and I have <choice><sic>bin</sic><corr>been</corr></choice> to see my famley they are well <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> are all m[o]unted an <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> have got the <choice><sic>pras</sic><corr>praise</corr></choice> of the finest <choice><sic>regment</sic><corr>regiment</corr></choice> in these pats My Capten Skaggs<ptr target="tex.00124_n2"/> is <choice><sic>ded</sic><corr>dead</corr></choice> brother <choice><sic>william</sic><corr>William</corr></choice><ptr target="tex.00124_n3"/> is very low<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>I</corr></choice><choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> think that he will live but 3 or <choice><sic>foar</sic><corr>four</corr></choice> days  <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> think we will <choice><sic>cros</sic><corr>cross</corr></choice> the Cumbrlen river in a few days <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> have got <choice><sic>plontloon</sic><corr>pontoon</corr></choice> &amp; boats in a <choice><sic>larg</sic><corr>large</corr></choice> <choice><sic>foars</sic><corr>fours</corr></choice> in an a bout here most of them is mounted <choice><sic>intfery</sic><corr>infantry</corr></choice> an <choice><sic>cavelry</sic><corr>cavalry</corr></choice> <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> think <choice><sic>wee</sic><corr>we</corr></choice> will make a <choice><sic>gard</sic><corr>guard</corr></choice> on nxvill [Knoxville?] excuse bad <choice><sic>riten</sic><corr>written</corr></choice> an short <choice><sic>leter</sic><corr>letter</corr></choice> yours <choice><sic>rspectivly</sic><corr>respectively</corr></choice></p>
            <p>Direct your <choice><sic>leter</sic><corr>letter</corr></choice> to Co E 2 <choice><sic>tennossee</sic><corr>Tennessee</corr></choice> <choice><sic>regment</sic><corr>regiment</corr></choice> <choice><sic>Conal</sic><corr>Colonel</corr></choice> Carter<ptr target="tex.00124_n4"/> Commanding</p>
         
